<ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">At least 10</ENAMEX> states are resisting <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Drexel Burnham Lambert Inc. 's</ENAMEX> nationwide effort to settle its legal troubles , and some might instead try to revoke the firm 's license to sell securities within their borders .
