<ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">Just yesterday</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">New Hampshire</ENAMEX> announced it made a $ <ENAMEX TYPE="MONEY">75,000</ENAMEX> settlement with <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Drexel</ENAMEX> , a record - tying fine for a securities - law matter in that state .
