<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Ohio</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">the District of Columbia</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Tennessee</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Illinois</ENAMEX> have been less resistant to <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Drexel</ENAMEX> than the other <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">six</ENAMEX> states , but nonetheless have refused to settle so far , say those familiar with the discussions .
